testcase.name: WORKFLOW_TESTS - 4 out of 4 - step workFlow tests Below test cases are for newVersionOnly settings S-WF-5859-001. User triggers a pipeline of two steps connected by a resource with newVersionOnly on the step following the resource and it does not update the resource. The first step is successful, the second skipped, and the run status is success.
